sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Nguoi dung
    participant FE as Chat UI
    participant API as Chat API
    participant DB as Conversation DB
    participant Search as Search/Analytics Index
    participant Admin as Admin UI

    U->>FE: Gui/nhan tin nhan
    FE->>API: Message event
    API->>DB: Upsert conversation, message, sender, timestamp, metadata
    API->>Search: Index noi dung va metadata
    API-->>FE: Ack/response
    Admin->>API: Truy xuat lich su theo user/session/keyword
    API->>DB: Lay conversation timeline
    API->>Search: Tim kiem neu co keyword/filter
    DB-->>API: Message history
    Search-->>API: Ket qua phu hop
    API-->>Admin: Hien thi lich su hoi thoai
